      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/paramount-will-let-exclusive-talks-with-skydance-lapse-nyt-reports-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《纽约时报》周五援引知情人士的话报道称，派拉蒙全球将结束与 Skydance Media 的独家谈判，但未达成协议。]]></description>
