      <title>派拉蒙将终止与 Skydance 的独家谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sony-apollo-submit-26-bln-paramount-offer-wsj-reports-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，派拉蒙全球公司将在未达成协议的情况下结束与 Skydance Media 的独家谈判，从而允许其评估对《碟中谍》和《海绵宝宝》拍摄地的竞争对手的竞标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sony-apollo-submit-26-bln-paramount-offer-wsj-reports-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 09:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
